npm init playwright this will genrate skeleton for your project

we have to install node.js before entering the above command

package.json file is more important it will contains all playwright dependent libraries.

all the playwright related jars will be stored in node_modules file.

All the configurations of tests will be configured on playwright.config.js file

Impoirtance of playwright.config.js

npx playwright test  this command will runner test runner file which is playwright.config.js

npx playwright test --headed this commnd will run all the cases in headed mode
npx playwright test --ui

It starts Playwright Test UI Mode, which gives you a visual interface in the browser to:
✅ See all test files and test cases
✅ Run tests one by one or in groups
✅ Watch tests execute step‑by‑step
✅ View screenshots, videos, and traces
✅ Debug failed tests very easily
✅ Re‑run tests without restarting the command

